Attached files provide summaries of the FY 2010 aggregate Federal Government and individual agency Scope 1,2 and 3 emissions. The inventories are broken into two data sets: one set of GHG emissions subject to reduction targets, and a separate data set of military operations, law enforcement, and other emissions not subject
